  <brief_title>Restrictive Versus Liberal Transfusion Protocol in Infants Undergoing Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial Comparing a Restrictive Versus Liberal Transfusion Strategy in Neonates and Infants Undergoing Surgery for Congenital Heart Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
